FLYING TIGER LINE
TOLE MASANSLOWAY WEST
COMMSSIS
CORPORATE LIBRARY
SEP 2, & 1980
PAN AMERICAN WORLD AIRWAYS
September 15, 1980
Attached is a copy of our General Schedule No. 64, replacing General
Schedule No. 63 and all its revisions.
This reflects the merger of The Flying Tiger Line and Seaboard
World Airlines. The flights in the United States and Asia are
effective September 29, 1980 and Europe flights are effective
October 1, 1980.
Many y to feich.
Mary Hadfield, Director
Schedule Planning
